This is a gentle reminder that your speech is scheduled for September 8th at 2:00 PM in the afternoon. We are reaching out to confirm your availability and to ensure that everything is set for your presentation. Should there be any changes to your plans or if you foresee any issues that might affect your participation, please do not hesitate to inform us at your earliest convenience. We appreciate your dedication to this cause and look forward to a fruitful event. Best regards, Linda Martin Event Coordinator Environmental Champions Phone: +1 (234) 567-8901 Email: linda.martin@environmentalchampions.org
